structure.unit: A KENTUCKY UNIFORM UNINCORPORATED NONPROFIT ASSOCIATION ACT

text.section: Principles of law and equity supplement this chapter unless displaced by a particular provision of it.
A statute governing a specific type of unincorporated nonprofit association prevails over an inconsistent provision in this chapter, to the extent of the inconsistency.

law.history: Created 2015 Ky. Acts ch. 34, sec. 41, effective June 24, 2015.
